</head>
<body>
  <div class="MainBody">
    <div class="header">
      <%- include('header') %>
    </div>
    <!-- Content for Home page goes here -->
    <div class="sideMenu">
        <p class="menu">Paw Menu</p>
        <!-- Navigation links to different pages -->
        <a href="/login">Login</a>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/pets">Browse Available Pets</a>
        <a href="/Find_DOG_CAT">Find a Dog/Cat</a>
        <a href="/Dog_Care">Dog Care</a>
        <a href="/Cat_Care">Cat Care</a>
        <a href="/register">Register</a>
        <a href="/rehabilitate">Have a pet to give away?</a>
        <a href="/Contact_Us">Contact Us</a>
        <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
      </div>
      <!-- MAIN CONTENT SECTION -->
      <div class="content">
        <p class="contentHeader">Welcome to The Concordia Paws</p>
        <!-- Image related to the main page, aligned to the right -->
        <img class="contentImageFloatRight" src="/images/mainhome.jpg" alt="MAIN PAGE IMAGE">
        <!-- Text content introducing the organization -->
        <p class="contentText">
          Welcome to The Concordia Paws, your trusted partner in finding loving homes for cats
          and dogs in need. Our mission is to connect compassionate families with their perfect
          pet companions, ensuring every animal gets the chance to experience a caring and
          nurturing environment. Browse our gallery of featured pets, use our advanced search
          to find your ideal match, and learn about our straightforward adoption process.
          Be inspired by our success stories and discover how you can support our mission
          through donations, volunteering, or fostering. Have questions or need assistance?
          Our friendly team is here to help you every step of the way. Start your journey with
          The Concordia Paws today and make a difference in a pet's life.
        </p>
        <!-- Additional text content providing more information about the organization -->
        <p class="contentText">
          At The Concordia Paws, we believe in the harmony and balance between humans and
          animals, inspired by our namesake, the goddess of the Earth. Our mascot,
          the greyhound, embodies loyalty, grace, and elegance, symbolizing the core
          values we hold dear. Every pet that comes through our doors receives the
          highest standard of care and love, preparing them for a seamless transition
          into their new homes. Whether you're looking for a playful kitten, a gentle
          senior dog, or anything in between, our diverse selection of pets ensures you'll
          find the perfect companion.
        </p>
        <!-- Information on available pets and how to adopt -->
        <p class="contentText">
          Explore our collection of pets currently <a href="/Find_DOG_CAT">available for adoption</a>
          and find your perfect companion. If you have specific preferences or requirements,
          you can easily submit an adoption form. The Concordia Paws is also committed to
          accepting animals in need of <a href="/rehabilitate">rehabilitation and rehoming</a>, ensuring they receive the best care possible.
        </p>
      </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <%- include('footer') %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
